summary:
At Snowflake our mission is to help every customer become a data-driven business. 

Snowflake is a cloud data platform that is disrupting how organizations traditionally manage their most important asset - data. We've removed the barriers of cost, time, and scale to enable near-limitless access to all sources and types of data.

Empowered with new and innovative insights from their data, our customers move from being fearful of disruption to confident data-driven disruptors.
